{"tid":133372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【差佬晒馬】長洲覆核王擬告一哥瀆職 縱容警隊非法集會","createTime":"2017-02-24T14:17:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-25T12:09:18.000Z","uid":48093,"like":88,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7c125d0e82395d22ddcbd98d4f7f557a8bca5411","tid":133372,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T14:17:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170224/large/1487945314_d23c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170224%2Flarge%2F1487945314_d23c.jpg&h=5b34e1bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有「長洲覆核王」之稱的郭卓堅計劃下周一上午向高等法院提出司法覆核，指控警務處處長盧偉聰涉嫌瀆職，縱容4個警察協會日前動員非法集會，批評盧偉聰作為處長縱容下屬違法。<br />\n<br />\n郭卓堅在申請司法覆核許司的通知書中，要求法庭頒令4個警察協會22日晚上舉行聲援入獄七警的「特別大會」是非法集會，違反《警察通例》6章34條及《公安條例》第7條，即超過500人的集會需事先向警方提出申請的規定。郭在通知書中批評盧偉聰作為警隊一哥，對事件「視而不見，容許下尉犯罪而不予譴責」，質疑對方干犯瀆職罪，並要求處分滋事份子。"},{"pid":"5502c504fde7eb5ffd783ab16fb37995026333f5","tid":133372,"uid":51828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T14:20:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4693b2f2a9a6b923af1b574f85db076e4797df0","tid":133372,"uid":31748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T14:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96c62d7ba389fe2dda4cb60b8e541bd661a3ff7d","tid":133372,"uid":16554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T14:22:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cacd316cd15a8fb46fe6744efd5b212ffc7cc756","tid":133372,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-24T14:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/l